please don't hang up.</i>

6
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:28,673
<i>Just talk to me, okay?
I can't believe you just left.</i>

7
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:31,068
<i>Michelle.</i>

8
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,273
<i>Come back.</i>

9
00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:36,872
<i>Please say something.</i>

10
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:40,555
<i>Michelle, talk to me.</i>

11
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,950
<i>Look, we had an argument.
Couples fight.</i>

12
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:46,713
<i>That is no reason
to just leave everything behind.</i>

13
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:51,349
<i>Running away isn't gonna help it any.
Michelle, please...</i>

14
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,519
(DIALTONE)

15
