16
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:02,675
<i>Elsewhere today,
power has still not been restored</i>

17
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:04,637
<i>to many cities on the southern seaboard</i>

18
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:07,280
<i>in the wake of
this afternoon's widespread blackout.</i>

19
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:09,715
<i>While there had been
some inclement weather in the region,</i>

20
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:11,472
<i>the problem seems linked to
what authorities are calling</i>

21
