48
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:02,672
(DOOR CREAKING)

49
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:16,551
Okay. Okay, please.

50
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:18,314
Please.

51
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:21,112
Please don't hurt me.

52
00:10:22,160 --> 00:10:23,354
